Class AeSchemaParserUtil

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.wsdl.def.castor.AeSchemaParserUtil
public class AeSchemaParserUtil
extends java.lang.Object

Utility methods for fixing up schema imports (either from wsdl files or from nested imports) so that schemas are accessible via URL.
